<p>Creating ‚ÄúWindows‚Äù in the DOM is something sensational, especially if you want to create online systems, online terminal or even an operating system prototype! üòÉ</p>

<p>And doing that now is even simpler with Winbox.js.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/js/winbox.png" alt="Winbox.js" /></p>

<!-- QUADRADO -->
<script async="" src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>

<p><ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:inline-block;width:336px;height:280px" data-ad-client="ca-pub-2838251107855362" data-ad-slot="5351066970"></ins>
