</script></p>

<p>WinBox is a modern HTML5 window manager for the web. Light and excellent performance, without dependencies, fully customizable, free and open source!</p>

<p>There are numerous ways to use it, such as:</p>

<p>Via npm:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">npm <span class="nb">install </span>winbox</code></pre></figure>

<p>Importing the module via CDN:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;script <span class="nb">type</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"module"</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
  import WinBox from <span class="s2">"https://unpkg.com/winbox@0.1.8/src/js/winbox.js"</span><span class="p">;</span>
&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre></figure>

<p>Or by downloading from the <a href="https://nextapps-de.github.io/winbox/">website</a>.</p>

